WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.234
Hey, good evening, everybody.

00:00:01.234 --> 00:00:06.625
I just wanted to come on here and talk to you all about some things the Lord has been speaking to me about through prayer.

00:00:07.055 --> 00:00:16.020
First off, I want to just say thank you for all the support that I'm getting, all the encouragement, and all the blessings—you all keep saying 'bless you' and all that stuff.

00:00:16.020 --> 00:00:23.360
There are several people who are not being too nice, but for the most part, I have a lot of support, so I just wanted to say thank you.

00:00:23.360 --> 00:00:25.097
I am not a fortune teller.

00:00:25.097 --> 00:00:32.399
Please do not email my house asking for direction concerning your life for me to hear God for you.

00:00:32.399 --> 00:00:36.980
My job is to come on here and teach you how to do it yourself.

00:00:36.980 --> 00:00:42.239
You have the same Holy Ghost that lives on the inside of you that lives on the inside of me.

00:00:42.549 --> 00:00:52.680
People are really concerned about the EMP attack; people are really concerned about the water poisoning.

00:00:52.680 --> 00:00:59.554
Whenever I was taking care of my yard work, the Lord spoke to me and said there's a shifting.

00:01:00.120 --> 00:01:07.157
I could feel it; there's a pushback of the demonic assignment that was upon America.

00:01:07.157 --> 00:01:13.920
Our prayers are working, and he reminded me, 'Brandon, I called you and put you on there for prayer.

00:01:13.920 --> 00:01:21.659
' That was your main assignment: to teach the people to pray, putting videos of prayer so that they could jump in the rivers.

00:01:21.659 --> 00:01:34.894
We are a mighty force together when we are praying as a unit, not like, as I said, Rambos out there trying to fight the war by themselves.

00:01:34.894 --> 00:01:47.292
If we will come together and fight together, we're able to move mountains, and it's amazing what we can accomplish just with five minutes of prayer a day.

00:01:47.292 --> 00:01:54.551
I'm not bringing it in, as I said, for fear; I'm bringing this to you to help me pray.

00:01:54.551 --> 00:01:55.358
It's not drama.

00:01:55.358 --> 00:02:02.940
So, here you go: I want to come on here and I want to tell you all some things now about what the Lord is showing me in prayer.

00:02:02.940 --> 00:02:09.497
First off, I want to tell you all some positive things, something that happened that was a birthday present to me from the Lord.

00:02:09.497 --> 00:02:15.735
When I was praying, all of a sudden, he said, 'I want to give you a birthday present, Brandon.

00:02:15.735 --> 00:02:20.933
' And I said, 'Oh, wow, what is it, Lord?

00:02:20.933 --> 00:02:30.780
' Then all of a sudden, he opened my eyes in the spirit and he showed me right after the Rapture happens.

00:02:30.780 --> 00:02:35.520
I was standing in heaven, and I was on this green field.

00:02:37.277 --> 00:02:37.654
It was beautiful.

00:02:37.654 --> 00:02:46.680
There were hills all up in front of me and I could see mountains all in the distance.

00:02:46.680 --> 00:02:55.065
There was snow on top of these mountains, which is really amazing.

00:02:56.790 --> 00:02:58.425
This was happening—it looked like the Swiss Alps.

00:03:03.134 --> 00:03:04.395
It was gorgeous all in the distance.

00:03:04.395 --> 00:03:07.560
These green pastures were all before me.

00:03:07.560 --> 00:03:11.312
The grass was so green it looked almost transparent.

00:03:18.960 --> 00:03:19.200
It was beautiful green grass.

00:03:23.494 --> 00:03:26.370
I have never seen this kind of grass on the earth, how beautiful and lush and green this was.

00:03:26.370 --> 00:03:30.420
My wife was running in from the distance and she was doing cartwheels.

00:03:34.169 --> 00:03:34.424
We were in our glorified bodies.

00:03:35.190 --> 00:03:44.219
I could see I was skinny and I had hair, but my face didn't look hard, as if I'd been through a lot.

00:03:44.219 --> 00:03:46.874
It was so young and youthful; it was beautiful.

00:03:52.660 --> 00:03:53.293
Everything I was seeing—I could see my wife, and she was doing cartwheels like I said.

00:03:53.293 --> 00:03:58.179
She ran into me and she goes, 'Brandon, we made it!

00:03:58.179 --> 00:03:59.433
It really happened.

00:03:59.433 --> 00:04:02.480
' And I kept saying, 'It really happened.

00:04:03.280 --> 00:04:03.480
We made it.

00:04:03.480 --> 00:04:06.893
' I could see the glory; you could feel the presence of glory.

00:04:06.893 --> 00:04:10.791
There were no shadows on anything; the light was so beautiful and so bright.

00:04:10.791 --> 00:04:15.839
Sorry, my dog is running in the back playing with a toy, if you heard that squeaking.

00:04:15.839 --> 00:04:18.929
There was a glorious light all around everything and heaven.

00:04:18.929 --> 00:04:23.775
I just wanted to come on and tell you all, we're about to be there.

00:04:23.775 --> 00:04:27.909
We're almost there; we're right at the finish line, guys.

00:04:27.909 --> 00:04:31.300
We just got to push just a little bit harder here.

00:04:31.300 --> 00:04:37.573
We got to pray, and God's going to do some great things in this earth still with a revival.

00:04:37.573 --> 00:04:45.250
There's going to be some people He's going to bring in that have been wayward—the children that are wayward.

00:04:45.250 --> 00:04:53.470
Like I said, the moms are praying, and they're calling out and asking God for their kids to get born again.

00:04:53.470 --> 00:04:59.146
I'm telling you, don't give up on those children that are wayward.

00:05:01.302 --> 00:05:04.283
The Lord hears your prayers, and He's bringing those kids in.

00:05:04.283 --> 00:05:13.710
I'm telling you, you just got to keep the faith and keep standing, and there's going to be a breakthrough in your household.

00:05:29.055 --> 00:05:29.190
I'm telling you, you just got to keep on.

00:05:29.190 --> 00:05:32.060
When all else there is to do is stand, stand therefore.

00:05:32.060 --> 00:05:39.150
Do not give up for your healings, for the miracles that you're believing for, or for finances.

00:05:39.150 --> 00:05:48.925
You may not have anything to eat, but my God said He's never seen the righteous forsaken or his seed begging bread.

00:05:48.925 --> 00:05:52.290
He'll bring forth the finances that you need.

00:06:02.966 --> 00:06:03.909
I just believe in a faithful God; if He would bring the raven to feed Elijah, He'll bring a raven to feed you.

00:06:03.909 --> 00:06:15.429
Now, I just want to tell you all what the Lord has warned me about what's coming and what we can avoid in prayer and what we can stop.

00:06:15.429 --> 00:06:17.268
Excuse me, I saw...

00:06:17.268 --> 00:06:22.279
this is something that reminded me when I was doing my yard work tonight.

00:06:24.262 --> 00:06:25.972
This is what I'm trying to tell you.

00:06:30.213 --> 00:06:32.031
He said, 'I want you to tell them to pray for Donald Trump.

00:06:32.031 --> 00:06:36.437
' I saw him walking down on a cobblestone path.

00:06:40.932 --> 00:06:42.863
I saw it was like tropical—I don't know where he was—but I saw a woman.

00:06:42.863 --> 00:06:45.863
Now, sometimes I'm seeing in the spirit and it's not necessarily...

00:06:50.730 --> 00:06:59.775
this warning that the Lord has told me about was about Donald Trump and to intercede and pray for him.

00:06:59.775 --> 00:07:04.200
He showed me him walking down a cobblestone path.

00:07:04.200 --> 00:07:11.280
Now, I don't know if this is legitimately a cobblestone path or if it's like a type and shadow of something.

00:07:11.280 --> 00:07:15.009
He's walking down this path, and this woman is absolutely beautiful.

00:07:15.343 --> 00:07:23.520
She has blonde hair in a French twist and she was dressed up in a beautiful dress.

00:07:23.520 --> 00:07:25.464
She was there to take him out.

00:07:27.796 --> 00:07:31.330
The Secret Service people around were not guarded because of this woman's beauty; she was very classy.

00:07:41.685 --> 00:07:43.773
I don't know if this is a type and shadow of someone who would try to seduce him, but this woman was an assignment against him.

00:07:51.355 --> 00:07:53.160
This is something I'm praying over: protection for God to deliver him from either a seducing spirit, like a Jezebel kind of person, or an actual attempt on him.

00:08:02.963 --> 00:08:03.191
This is very serious.

00:08:07.780 --> 00:08:11.143
The Lord has had me praying for his protection from an assignment involving this beautiful woman.

00:08:11.143 --> 00:08:14.912
She has blonde hair and looks very much like a model.

00:08:14.912 --> 00:08:17.780
This was part of something the Lord had me interceding for.

00:08:17.780 --> 00:08:25.530
Lately, He had me praying for this oil tanker that was in the Atlantic Ocean coming out of Africa.

00:08:25.530 --> 00:08:32.279
This is something else; it's not about fear, it's just something I pray over.

00:08:42.419 --> 00:08:42.719
You are prayer warriors, and you can help me.

00:08:45.873 --> 00:08:50.160
This could be something way off in the distance or something we've already stopped, but I bring these things out here.

00:08:50.160 --> 00:08:58.340
If you feel led to pray over it, pray; if not, put it on a shelf and walk away.

00:08:58.340 --> 00:09:06.360
This was an oil tanker coming out of Africa, and all of the crew on board were rounded up by these terrorists.

00:09:06.360 --> 00:09:12.540
They were hiding on the ship, got on board, took these men to the bottom of the ship, and killed them.

00:09:20.430 --> 00:09:20.715
I saw them with a briefcase—I'm not going to say the word—but it's very powerful.

00:09:20.715 --> 00:09:24.044
They took the ship to Washington Harbor, near Virginia.

00:09:24.044 --> 00:09:28.073
I'm going to show you on a map right now.

00:09:28.073 --> 00:09:31.834
They brought the ship in and set this thing off.

00:09:31.834 --> 00:09:35.812
It was very serious and powerful; everything went away.

00:09:35.812 --> 00:09:41.020
I'm trying to say this in a way that doesn't get me flagged.

00:09:41.020 --> 00:09:48.386
I just wanted to come on here and tell you these are more things I'm praying over.

00:09:48.386 --> 00:09:52.080
We live in dangerous and challenging times.

00:09:52.080 --> 00:10:00.060
I do not live in a fairytale land where everything is always okay.

00:10:00.060 --> 00:10:06.711
I wake up every day and the Lord has me on assignments.

00:10:22.967 --> 00:10:23.380
I am on missions, praying for things on a continual basis for what He has for the end times, for the church, and for the thousand years.

00:10:23.380 --> 00:10:29.982
We have a bright future ahead of us; God has a great plan for us.

00:10:29.982 --> 00:10:34.740
Lastly, He had me pray against large gatherings of people for mass shootings.

00:10:34.740 --> 00:10:39.818
Pray against this; it's an assignment being sent to try to take the Second Amendment away from the people.

00:10:39.818 --> 00:10:49.659
And they're going to run on campaigns in 2024; a lot of it will be ran against the Second Amendment and taking things away.

00:10:52.500 --> 00:10:53.513
I saw these big mass events trying to take place.

00:11:10.013 --> 00:11:10.386
The Lord had me pray very hard for Coachella.

00:11:10.386 --> 00:11:17.640
I kept praying for this word, 'Coachella,' and I kept getting this in the spirit realm.

00:11:17.640 --> 00:11:27.480
So I told my friend about it and he helped me Google it, and then my wife helped me Google this word.

00:11:27.720 --> 00:11:33.600
It was days away from what was supposed to take place, and I interceded for this hard.

00:11:33.600 --> 00:11:39.342
I prayed a fast, believing God for protection so that this stuff didn't happen.

00:11:39.342 --> 00:11:40.885
Nothing happened.

00:11:40.885 --> 00:11:46.567
Now, I don't know when it happens again; I believe probably next year.

00:11:46.567 --> 00:11:51.900
So we're going to pray that these major events and big gatherings of people for nothing to happen.

00:11:51.900 --> 00:11:57.217
If you have a check in your spirit about major gatherings, do not go.

00:11:57.217 --> 00:11:59.920
Pray in the Holy Ghost and the Lord will protect you.

00:11:59.920 --> 00:12:06.578
Use wisdom in this day and hour for you and for your family to not just be flippantly going places.

00:12:06.578 --> 00:12:13.379
Pray ahead of time: 'Lord, is it Your will for me to go to that concert?

00:12:13.379 --> 00:12:19.807
Is it Your will for me to go to that sporting event?

00:12:19.807 --> 00:12:28.097
' Because if you don't and you hear the Lord not to go, it could cost you your life.

00:12:29.004 --> 00:12:36.620
You have to be very vigilant nowadays in prayer and fasting, listening to Him on where you're supposed to be at all times.

00:12:36.620 --> 00:12:42.033
Don't just go to malls; do not just go to certain things without hearing Him on that day.

00:12:42.033 --> 00:12:46.340
Wake up that morning and say, 'Father, what am I supposed to do?

00:12:46.340 --> 00:12:49.113
What's Your agenda for me, not what's my agenda?

00:12:49.113 --> 00:12:53.483
' You listen to Him for your life.

00:12:53.483 --> 00:12:56.399
'Lord, can I go to the grocery store today?

00:12:56.399 --> 00:12:58.008
Can I go to the game?

00:12:58.008 --> 00:13:01.140
Can I go to this and that?

00:13:01.140 --> 00:13:09.307
' Ask Him; He will guide you on every step you're supposed to take for your life that day, every day.

00:13:17.355 --> 00:13:17.602
He wants to be that close to you.

00:13:17.602 --> 00:13:19.919
Let Him speak to you and practice His presence.

00:13:19.919 --> 00:13:24.667
A lot of people always ask me, 'How do you hear God the way you do?

00:13:24.667 --> 00:13:27.686
How do you listen to Him like that?

00:13:27.686 --> 00:13:29.484
' It started like this.

00:13:29.676 --> 00:13:36.839
He told me, 'I'm going to start talking to you about things, and I want you to practice My voice.

00:13:38.130 --> 00:13:38.904
I want you to practice this.

00:13:38.904 --> 00:13:47.833
' It was just private between me and Him, and He said, 'I'm going to tell you about sports because I love sports.

00:13:47.833 --> 00:13:52.394
' It's one of my big things—football, basketball, baseball, all of it.

00:13:52.394 --> 00:13:57.105
I watch it, I love it, it's amazing to me.

00:13:57.105 --> 00:14:01.515
You know, just the game; I love the testosterone of it.

00:14:08.490 --> 00:14:08.820
And so, we would sit on the couch together, the Lord and I, and He would talk to me about the score.

00:14:08.820 --> 00:14:17.176
He'd say, 'This is who's going to win, and this is the score, and this is how much they're going to win by—this team and this team.

00:14:17.176 --> 00:14:27.420
' He'd tell me the game for that day, college football or whatever, and He said, 'This is who's going to win it, and this is how much they're going to win it by.

00:14:27.420 --> 00:14:36.259
' He talked about Super Bowls, He talks about World Series, He talks about it all.

00:14:40.747 --> 00:14:40.950
And so I practice His presence; I practice His voice.

00:14:40.950 --> 00:14:48.111
He said to me, 'If you ever bet or gamble on anything I ever tell you, I will not talk this way to you ever again.

00:14:48.111 --> 00:14:53.600
But I want you to go like you're going to a spiritual gym.

00:15:03.157 --> 00:15:03.450
I want you to work out that muscle, your spiritual ears, with Me.

00:15:03.450 --> 00:15:08.040
' And this is how I started: I practice His presence.

00:15:08.040 --> 00:15:12.345
Then He talks to me about the weather.

00:15:23.498 --> 00:15:23.820
He says, 'In six weeks, it's going to be this temperature outside; it's going to snow, and this is how much we're going to get.

00:15:23.820 --> 00:15:28.200
' He talks to me about how much rain we're going to get.

00:15:28.200 --> 00:15:34.459
He talks to me about when the fall will start, when the first cold front's going to come, and He tells me way in advance.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
He said, 'I want you to write this down.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:11.900
' He said summer's going to have this many hurricanes, and in the Gulf Coast, this is how many hurricanes are going to be here and this is how big they're going to be.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
You can pray against them, pray for safety for people, and He will show me.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
Then He shows me about tornado season; He shows me about the storms.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
That's how I've learned to develop my spiritual ears, practicing His presence.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
And sometimes you miss it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
It's okay; we're human.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
But you just keep picking yourself back up and say, 'Lord, I missed that.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
I thought I heard You right on that, but I didn't.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
' And you humble yourself and you keep going.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
You don't kick yourself when you fall down; you rise back up.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
You have to keep on keeping on.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
We all have a tendency; we can miss it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.500
I'm going to tell you right off: I've missed it a lot on things when I was first starting out, about investments and the timing of things, and it's okay.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
That's how we learn.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
I just want to encourage you all.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
God is a graceful God.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
He's not mad; he's not up there beating people up.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
He is a lot of love.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
I just wanted to encourage you with that.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
That was another thing I wanted to tell you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
Have a blessed day, everybody.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye-bye.
